# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Simulate the process until there is at least 1 swap.
# Complexity
- Time complexity:O(N^2)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity:O(1)
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

# Code
```
class Solution {
public:
    int solve(string &s)
    {
        int i = 1,n = s.size(),fleg = 1;
        while(i<n)
        {
            if(s[i]=='1' && s[i-1]=='0')
            {
                swap(s[i],s[i-1]);
                fleg = 0;
                i+=2;
            }
            else
            i+=1;
        }
        if(fleg) return 0;
        return 1+solve(s);
    }
    int secondsToRemoveOccurrences(string s) {
        return solve(s);
    }
};
```
