# Approach
Simply har baar string mein last se traverse karke check karenge ki kya '01' present hai agar present hai toh replacements karne honge warna number of seconds ko return kardenge. Code mein comments ke through explain kiya hai ek baar read karo and dry run karo saath mein ek case lekar.
