This question can be easily done by prefix-sum array but here I want to give an approach of sqaure root decomposition. First of all learning sqaure root decomposition is an way to solve range queries question. Generally this has time complexity of sqrt(n)*n;
l=shifts[i][0];
r=shifts[i][1];

Prerequiste : Sqaure Root Decomposition 

All the questions of SQRTD has a common structure so learning only question will push you to solve this one.
