Every remove one element, remove the interval of it. And may add two intervals [left,k-1],[k+1,right]. 
one map store<sum of interval, numbers of sum>, one map store <left index,sum of interval>. That is to erase sum of interval according it's left index, and get max sum of interval in O(1).
