*Python* w/ prefix sum

```python
def maximumSegmentSum(self, nums, removeQueries):
    res, seen, psum = [0], {}, list(itertools.accumulate(nums, initial=0))
    for i in removeQueries[:0:-1]:                      # iterate reversely
        l, r = seen.get(i - 1, i), seen.get(i + 1, i)   # find leftmost and rightmost for current conjuntion
        seen[l], seen[r] = r, l                         # mark and merge segments from leftmost to rightmost
        res.append(max(res[-1], psum[r + 1] - psum[l])) # maximize segment sum from leftmost to rightmost
    return res[::-1]
```

