* **Approach :**
	* There are three cases for this problem -
		i) Training for Energy gain.
		ii) Traing for Experience gain.
		iii) Defeating the opponents
	* For case - i :
		* Training hours required, hours += energy[i] - initialEnergy + 1
		* Energy gained, initialEnergy +=  .energy[i] - initialEnergy + 1
	* For case - ii :
		* Training hours required, hours += experience[i] - initialExperience + 1
		* Experience gained, initialExperience += experience[i] - initialExperience + 1
	* For case - iii :
		* Experience will increase, initialExperience += experience[i]
		* Energy will decrease, initialEnergy -= energy[i]
	* Finally return the ans (hours).

* **Code :**
